```markdown
# Site Inspector - Blazor WebAssembly App

## Project Overview
A mobile-first PWA for construction site safety inspections. Inspectors fill out checklists, take photos, and sync data when connectivity is available.

## Architecture
- **Render Mode**: Interactive WebAssembly (all UI runs client-side)
- **Server Project** (`SiteInspector/`): Hosts the Blazor app, provides sync API endpoints
- **Client Project** (`SiteInspector.Client/`): Contains all interactive components, services, and offline logic
- **Storage**: IndexedDB via JS interop for offline-first local storage
- **Sync**: Automatic background sync when online, manual sync button available
- **PWA**: Service worker for offline asset caching

## Key Directories
- `SiteInspector.Client/Models/` — Data models (Inspection, ChecklistItem, InspectionPhoto, etc.)
- `SiteInspector.Client/Services/` — Business logic (IndexedDbService, SyncService, ConnectivityService)
- `SiteInspector.Client/Pages/` — Razor pages (Home, Sites, NewInspection, Checklist, InspectionDetail, PhotoCapture)
- `SiteInspector.Client/Layout/` — MainLayout with bottom navigation
- `SiteInspector.Client/wwwroot/js/` — JavaScript interop files (indexedDb.js, connectivity.js)
- `SiteInspector.Client/wwwroot/css/` — Mobile-first CSS styles

## Build & Run
```bash
dotnet build SiteInspector.sln
dotnet run --project SiteInspector/SiteInspector.csproj
```

## Design Decisions
- **Offline-first**: All data stored in IndexedDB, syncs when online
- **No authentication**: Simplified for field use
- **Large touch targets**: Minimum 48px for all interactive elements
- **Bottom navigation**: Mobile UX pattern for thumb-reachable navigation
- **Base64 photos**: Stored directly in IndexedDB for simplicity
- **Template checklists**: Pre-defined safety categories populated on new inspection

## API Endpoints
- `POST /api/sync/inspections` — Upload completed inspection
- `POST /api/sync/photos` — Upload inspection photos
- `GET /api/sync/status` — Check sync status

## Testing
Run `dotnet build` to verify compilation. The app requires a browser with IndexedDB support for full functionality.
```

